\f0\fs24 \cf0 #Financial Sentiment Analysis\
\
A web application that uses machine learning and natural language processing in order to perform financial sentiment analysis to analyze news headlines and calculate a sentiment score. This sentiment score is obtained from getting up-to-date news headlines using the newapi to update the score every time it is called upon and uses a sentiment analysis machine learning model to determine whether the headlines of the day are positive neutral or negative based on the weighted average of all the headlines\'92 sentiments. The web application can also analyze any headline you paste into the input field where you can try out the financial sentiment analysis for yourself. \
