\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 ## Features - Analyze real-time financial sentiment from news headlines. - Input custom headlines to determine their sentiment. - Display sentiment scores (positive, neutral, or negative). - Weighted sentiment scoring to reflect optimism or pessimism accurately.\
