## Technologies Used - **Frontend**: HTML, CSS, JavaScript (for UI and interactivity) - **Backend**: Flask (Python) - **Machine Learning**: - Model: XGBoost Classifier - Text Vectorization: TF-IDF - Data Augmentation: SMOTE - **APIs**: News API for fetching real-time financial news - **Libraries**: - Pandas, Numpy (data processing) - Scikit-learn, NLTK (machine learning and preprocessing)\
